DESCRIPTION:MAP's sculpture courtyard transforms into a garden with Living Botanicals — a space where plants native to the subcontinent grow\, change\, and are cared for over time.\n\nJoin us for a guided walk led by architect Bhavana Kumar of Kumar La Noce and urban gardener Kush Sethi as they share the process and vision behind this living installation.
DTEND:20260228T063000Z
